{"id": "art-25127", "label": "Art. 25127", "title": "Art. 25127", "slug": "art-25127", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1703758065\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1651\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1703758065\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>27</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_979003034\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1650\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_979003034\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Expertul independent/<span class=SpellE>Exper&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>independen&#355;i</span> care elaboreaz&#259; raportul\nprev&#259;zut la art. 251<sup>26</sup> alin. (1) este evaluator autorizat/sunt\nevaluatori <span class=SpellE>autoriza&#355;i</span> potrivit <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1138105791\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1649\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1138105791\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Evaluatorul\nautorizat este independent <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> participante la fuziune <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, în realizarea evalu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunii</span>,\nnu se afl&#259; în conflict de interese cu societatea. Nu poate elabora\nraportul de evaluare privitor la fuziunea transfrontalier&#259; evaluatorul\nautorizat care se afl&#259; în una dintre urm&#259;toarele <span class=SpellE>circumstan&#355;e</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_166088415\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1648\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_166088415\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)are/a avut calitatea de asociat, administrator,\ndirector/membru al directoratului, membru al consiliului de supraveghere în\ncadrul oric&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nparticipante la fuziunea transfrontalier&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_373341089\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1647\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_373341089\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)a avut, într-o perioad&#259; de 2 ani anterioar&#259;\ndatei solicit&#259;rii de evaluare, calitatea de auditor financiar, expert\ncontabil, contabil autorizat al oric&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nparticipante la fuziunea transfrontalier&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1499407940\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1646\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1499407940\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)a avut, într-o perioad&#259; de 2 ani anterioar&#259;\ndatei solicit&#259;rii de evaluare, raporturi de munc&#259; cu oricare dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> participante la fuziunea\ntransfrontalier&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_580164959\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1645\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_580164959\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)are un interes personal, de natur&#259; patrimonial&#259;\nsau nepatrimonial&#259;, care ar putea <span class=SpellE>influen&#355;a</span>\n<span class=SpellE>impar&#355;ialitatea</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nobiectivitatea evalu&#259;rii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1148387878\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1644\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1148387878\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)La raportul de evaluare se anexeaz&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span> pe propria r&#259;spundere a evaluatorului\nautorizat privind întrunirea <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span> legale\npentru întocmirea raportului de evaluare a fuziunii transfrontaliere.</span></p>"}